 <h1>Home Teacher Programs</h1>

<p><strong>Do you want to gain valuable experience as an international traveler and educator? Need job experience as a teacher? This program is designed for college educated individuals to travel overseas as home teachers and live with a European family!</strong><br />
</p>
<p><strong>Accomodation / Meals / Duration:</strong>&nbsp;Participants stay with a host family who provide them with full board and a single room. The program is available for one, two or three months, between April and September in France & Belgium, and all year round in Italy.</p>

<p><strong>Terms of Participation:</strong></p>
<ul><li> Be between 21 and 30 years old
<li> Have a good knowledge of French / Italian
<li> Be a graduated or currently enrolled in Higher Education / University, in and education-related field
<li> Relevany Experience is a bonus
<li> Be a European citizen or able to get a visa &quot;waiver&quot; that allows a stay in France, Belgium or Italy for three months
<li> Have travel insurance covering sickness, accidents, repatriatrion and third party liability</li>
</ul>

